project: Tell a Friend or Seek Help

Gips is known as the quiet kid at school. He is often bullied and refers to his bullies as pigs. One day, he decides he can't take it anymore and plans to get revenge on them. However, as he starts down this path, he realizes he might be his own worst enemy.
Gips starts plotting his revenge against the bullies. He knows where they live and plans to wreak havoc on their houses.
Gips talks to a friend about the bullying. His friend advises him to either confront the bullies or report them to a teacher.
